{"tid":609261,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人啲同事同我一樣，唔講是非佢就冇話題？","createTime":"2018-03-29T01:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T05:06:44.000Z","uid":169392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8d5d825cab18310a5c290601a5afa751129b34","tid":609261,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T01:39:32.000Z","msg":"我間公司啲同事係啲四五十歲嘅清潔廢老閪女人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地一講是非就會好撚high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講唔撚停。<br />\n長氣又尋氣，將一件事講幾百萬次，<br />\n見每一個唔同嘅人都會重複不停去講。<br />\n但你會發現佢地除咗講人是非之外，<br />\n佢地係冇其他話題... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，佢地好撚鐘意係公司搞分化，<br />\n總之就覺得只有佢地圍內班清潔閪就係最撚好咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗：你班廢老人生除咗番工之外，<br />\n你係咪冇其他興趣或者活動？<br />\n好可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每次對住佢地就好心煩<br />\n正一垃圾廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4782c18fd28e69f526af241b43547a21090f4d4","tid":609261,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a27b0c2d4d3b789fd7cddb3dfbdf56d579e13a","tid":609261,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"佢地係要見到人地之間不和  A唔妥B  C講返A壞話<br />\n自己企中間食花生扮知好多野<br />\n從中取得存在感"},{"pid":"977d30f5b4f4098fe641326af800a75a74e881ec","tid":609261,"uid":167757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明白講事非班人講出黎係咩心態<br />\nr水吹又唔似。<br />\n定係想人地覺得佢係萬事通知好多野？"},{"pid":"ff827394acdba7dbd12a9a1e7c23878ec7db0d65","tid":609261,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係好明白講事非班人講出黎係咩心態<br />\nr水吹又唔似。<br />\n定係想人地覺得佢係萬事通知好多野？</blockquote><br />\n咪係，應該係拎人地嘅事黎增加自己存在感"},{"pid":"1ac66fd7205b953b0e9d246950486f613e23a6e8","tid":609261,"uid":169392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:06:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地係要見到人地之間不和  A唔妥B  C講返A壞話<br />\n自己企中間食花生扮知好多野<br />\n從中取得存在感</blockquote><br />\n好變態嘅諗法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}